name: Frames
tagline: A library designed for game 2d UI layout. It is still under heavy development.
body:
Frame is an in-development UI library. It can be used under the GPL. Commercial licensing may be available later (if you're interested, send me an email.)

It is currently highly undocumented and provides no guarantees of backwards compatibility.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
